{"tid":1412486,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"入 黎 重 溫 下 推 動 大 家 繼 續 行 落 去 既 理 由","createTime":"2019-08-05T06:48:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T06:53:31.000Z","uid":211565,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"484bf3391c7dc00ede6624835c25692fa04f0757","tid":1412486,"uid":211565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T06:48:56.000Z","msg":"可能有人會開始覺得迷惘<br />\n覺得個社會好陌生<br />\n開始覺得有啲迷失<br />\n咁不如等我地黎討論下我地既初衷吖？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>五大訴求：</strong><br />\n<br />\n1. 撤回《逃犯條例》修訂；<br />\n2. 撤回 6.12 暴動定性；<br />\n3. 撤銷所有抗爭者控罪，不可秋後算帳；<br />\n4. 成立獨立調查委員會，調查警察濫暴濫權、追究警察開槍責任及元朗警黑勾結；<br />\n5. 全面落實雙普選。</span><br />\n<br />\n我地行過既路：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cGdNk5f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcGdNk5f.png&h=ec2e377f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n然而得到既回應...我相信大家有目共睹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後慢慢地導致後來既行動升級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>重點回顧：</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PX6K7Qf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPX6K7Qf.png&h=ab5efb40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n七月二十一號<br />\n元朗<span style=\"color: red;\">恐怖襲擊</span>+警察遲到39分鐘<br />\n上環<span style=\"color: purple;\">無警示下連開三十六槍</span><br />\n<br />\n七月三十一號<br />\n狂徒<span style=\"color: purple;\">向包圍天水圍警署既民眾發射煙花，多人被燒傷</span><br />\n <br />\n八月四號<br />\n觀塘警署<span style=\"color: red;\">派出狙擊手暗殺圍觀街坊</span><br />\n絕對冇警示冇舉旗<br />\n天水圍少女<span style=\"color: red;\">被警抬走時遭扯下內褲</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>關於市民人身安全：</strong><br />\n多次<span style=\"color: purple;\">於民居施放催淚彈</span>(元朗、黃大仙、港島西)<br />\n<br />\n攻擊無辜市民 令大眾生命安全受到威脅<br />\n將軍澳<span style=\"color: purple;\">居民下樓散步被警棍擊中</span> 頭破血流 -<span style=\"color: pink;\">香港電台-港聞</span><br />\n仲有rthk食飯街坊被速龍打頸既片 <br />\n但我暫時未搵得返係邊度睇<br />\n<br />\n<strong>關於新聞自由：</strong><br />\n記者群遭噴椒擲催淚彈 背心燒焦-明報<br />\n城大電台記者中催淚彈三級燒傷 擬向警索償-聯合報<br />\n警方以警棍驅趕記者-RTHK VNEWS<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/logged_out/watch/?video_id=2127038900929279&amp;refsrc=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2FRTHKVNEWS%2Fvideos%2F2127038900929279%2F&amp;_rdr\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Flogged_out%2Fwatch%2F%3Fvideo_id%3D2127038900929279%26refsrc%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fm.facebook.com%252FRTHKVNEWS%252Fvideos%252F2127038900929279%252F%26_rdr&d=7QdSi1Eq0NVbLWVUesVCWHG9l5Y5fMjkJfB04Oq%2Bkmk%3D&h=709c9aed\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/logged_out/watch/?video_id=2127038900929279&amp;refsrc=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2FRTHKVNEWS%2Fvideos%2F2127038900929279%2F&amp;_rdr</a></span><br />\n<br />\n元朗：<br />\n《立場》記者受傷<span style=\"color: purple;\"> 右肩需縫四針</span>-立場報導<br />\nNow新聞台一名攝影師採訪期間，遭到數名穿白衣人襲擊，<span style=\"color: purple;\">攝影機亦被擲至粉碎</span>-頭條新聞<br />\n<br />\n人道精神方面未有整理，歡迎大家補充<br />\n<br />\n最後希望大家係keep到你團火既同時<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">保持清醒 行動對準政權</span><br />\n唔好被憤怒衝昏頭腦為做而做 <br />\n我地要施壓既<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">係政府 唔係市民</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">小弟只係輕輕整理左一下 <br />\n，資料並唔完整，希望大家可以幫手補充/整理開新po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n另外有部份資料係喺朋友度cap，搵唔到出處，希望原作者屌得輕手啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"17ecf31747e64b49bb570ce4fcaa5c4261175daf","tid":1412486,"uid":211565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T06:50:34.000Z","msg":"點解要繼續？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">政府未回應五大訴求啊</span></span>"},{"pid":"1832b76c0d34275df5d3895cf42eb41ed6f6f2da","tid":1412486,"uid":211565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T06:51:14.000Z","msg":"點解要繼續？<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">因為公義未得彰顯啊</span></span>"},{"pid":"58d5bdea4677829f206bdb596062d505a0ff